data.allRelevantTextIncludingURLs: The upcoming live music events include the 'Drinking Boys and Girls Choir' concert on Sat, Nov 16 at the Mission Theater in Portland. Tickets can be purchased [here](https://www.etix.com/ticket/p/41479390/drinking-boys-and-girls-choirall-ages-portland-mcmenamins-mission-theater?partner_id=100). For more information about the event, visit [this link](https://monqui.com/event/drinkingboysandgirlsclub/mission-theater/portland-oregon/). Additionally, another event featuring 'Shallou' is also scheduled for Sat, Nov 16 at The Get Down, with tickets available [here](https://monqui.com/event/shallou-2/the-get-down/portland-oregon/).
